model_contributors: Katharine Sherratt, Nikos Bosse, Sam Abbott, Joel Hellewell, Sophie Meakin, James Munday, Sebastian Funk
Model_targets: time-varying reproduction number (Rt), deaths
Target_loc: US state + national
time_horizon: 4 weeks ahead
Data_format: all requested quantiles
forecast_startdate: 2020-06-15
forecast_frequency: weekly

data_inputs_known: 
data_source_known: 

this_model_is_an_ensemble: true
this_model_is_unconditional: true

methods: >-
    An ensemble forecast combining two models based on reported deaths data (Rt-based models and time series models).

methods_long: >-
    June 10: This ensemble forecast combines (1) Rt-based forecasts derived from reported deaths (Rt is estimated using EpiEstim and forecast using time series models; these forecasts of Rt are transformed into forcasted deaths using the renewal eqution), and (2) ARIMA time series models using reported deaths.